api.finance.yahoo.histquote

Class FYHistoricalQuotes

  • java.lang.Object
    • api.finance.yahoo.histquote.FYHistoricalQuotes

  • public class FYHistoricalQuotes
extends java.lang.Object
    Yahoo Finance Historical Quotes For example: Request: URL Response: JSON Alternate request: URL Response: CSV Supported intervals: 1m, 2m, 5m, 15m, 30m, 60m, 90m, 1h, 1d, 5d, 1wk, 1mo, 3mo Start date (period1) and end date (period2) are UNIX timestamps (seconds since January 1, 1970) Check URL
    Since:
    2018-02-10
    Version:
    1.3.0
    Author:
    mnemotron
